Thanks to another member for giving me a bunch of tips and locations to make my trip a lot of fun!! He knows who he is, and helped me out a lot via PM for this trip. Thanks again!!!
In my trip I caught over 20 specks but only took pictures of a few then my camera battery died. I also saw 2 rattle snakes and 1 garter snake which was neat.
Those rattlesnake pics are nice. Next time a few more closeups...No one has died of a Massasauga bite in a very long time.
Great snake pics!!!! Yet to see one !
Great pictures. Only ever seen one of those snakes well I was cliff jumping at oastler PP. kinda startled me
I wanted to get a few more pictures, but I was told that the little ones are stupid and will bite, so I chickened out lol.
Nice to see it went well,  I would've chickened out too!
